Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月的房間…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇君！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是…美月吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在做夢吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也真的是勇君嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯！就是我 勇鬥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇君…我好想見妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見妳啊 勇君…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
